dct_title_s: General-Karte des Königreiches Griechenland : im Masse 1:300 000 der Natur
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Title from sheet XI of main map, originally issued in 1885. in upper left margin: Klappe zu Bl. XI. In right lower margin: Gedruckt am 15/10. 1897. "Photolithographie und Schnellpressendruck." Supplement to map of Greece originally issued on 13 sheets, showing the Cyclades.
